rows.label: qst202902_msg0001
rows.name: What, a visitor at this hour?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0003
rows.name: How unusual. Please, come in.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm sorry to bother you
so late...[ML:Dash ] Is there someone
named Tsuki-san here?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0004
rows.name: That's me. Can I help you?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0005
rows.name:
Actually, my daughter
Kastina hasn't come home.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0006
rows.name:
I heard she spoke with you
the other day, so I thought
you might know something...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202902_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, that little girl who
took a shine to her...

rows.label: qst202902_msg0008
rows.name: She did ask Tsuki a lot of questions.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0009
rows.name: She did...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202902_msg0010
rows.name: [ML:Dash ][ML:Dash ]Could it be...?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0011
rows.name:
Maybe that child went
looking for Moondrops.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0012
rows.name:
I told her you can only
see them at night...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202902_msg0013
rows.name:
Then is Kastina outside
of Teos Aure right now?!

rows.label: qst202902_msg0014
rows.name: I can't say for sure, but...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202902_msg0022
rows.name: it's probably my fault...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202902_msg0015
rows.name:
Ma'am...[ML:Dash ] I'll go look for
Kastina, so please wait here.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0016
rows.name: I understand...[ML:Dash ] Please!

rows.label: qst202902_msg0017
rows.name:
Perhaps Kastina's friends
know where she went.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0023
rows.name: I came here first, so...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202902_msg0024
rows.name:
I'll ask them first. Ma'am...[ML:Dash ] could
you tell me her friends' names?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0018
rows.name:
Celesmia-san is in the Teos Aure
Residential Area, Manegal-kun
is in the Soprac Old Market,

rows.label: qst202902_msg0019
rows.name:
and Lieselotte-san should
be in Elmos Square.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0020
rows.name:
Thank you. I will bring
Kastina back, I promise...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202902_msg0021
rows.name: Please wait here.
